TextEng: Who are you?
I'd like to ask you some questions.
I need directions.
Who you?
Me have questions.
Me need directions. Is big place.
Text: 나 길 필요. 여기 큰 곳.

TextEng: Goodbye.
I'm called <FirstName>.
My name is <FullName>. I'm an adventurer.
I don't generally give out my name.
Go soak your head. I'm not telling you who I am.
Text: 머리나 식혀. 내가 누군지 안 알려 줄 거야.

TextEng: Me is <FirstName>.
Me called <FullName>. Me be big adventurer.
Me not usually say.
You get lost, me not telling.
What kind of job?
What job you speak of?
How do you intend to get me into the prison?
That doesn't seem like much pay for a lot of work.
Text: 많은 일에 비해 보수가 적어 보이는데.

TextEng: Perhaps you'd be willing to give an advance... ?
What dangers are you aware of?
All right, I guess I'm your <man/woman>.
No, I'm not interested in this.
How you get me into dis prison, anyway?
Not much pay for lots work.
Maybe you give some gold now... ?
Text: 지금 금화 좀 줄 수 있어...?

TextEng: What dangers dere be?
Okay, me do it.
No, me no do dis stuff.
What was it you needed doing again?
Something was controlling Head Gaoler Alaefin. I've got a piece of it.
Text: 뭔가가 간수장 알레핀을 조종하고 있었어요. 그녀석의 일부를 가지고 왔죠.

TextEng: Yes, I've changed my mind. I'll do it.
No, I'm still not interested.
What you want again?
Head Guy Alaefin was controlled by thingy. Me kill it, and got piece.
Text: 간수장 알레핀, 뭔가에 조종당했어. 내가 그 조각 하나 가졌어.

TextEng: Yes, me want to do it now.
No, me still not interested.
Yes, that will do nicely.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> I went through considerable trouble to get this... wouldn't a higher reward be suitable?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 이걸 얻느라 상당한 고생을 했는데... 더 높은 보상이 적절하지 않을까?

TextEng: Better offer some more money, woman. I'd hate for you to... come to harm.
Text: 돈을 좀 더 내는 게 좋을 거야. 당신한테... 나쁜 일이 생기는 건 원치 않으니까.

TextEng: Yuh, dat amount be okay.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me have hard time taking dis. Bigger reward be better, yuh?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 이거 얻느라 힘들었어. 보상 더 많으면 좋겠어, 알지?

TextEng: You give more gold or me get angry, start killin' more den just pris'ners!
Text: 금 더 줘, 안 그러면 나 화나서 죄수들보다 더 많이 죽일 거야!

TextEng: I need no reward. The Prison's troubles have been resolved and that is all that matters.
Text: 보상은 필요 없어. 감옥 문제가 해결됐고, 그것만으로 충분해.

TextEng: Me no need gold. Prison stuff fixed now, dat's all wut's important.
Text: 나 금 필요 없어. 감옥 일 해결됐어, 그게 제일 중요해.

TextEng: Head Gaoler Alaefin was controlled by something.
I'll get back to it. Farewell.
I'm not interested anymore.
Gaoler guy Alaefin controlled by nasty creature.
Text: 간수장 놈 알레핀, 더러운 놈이 조종했어.

TextEng: Me get back to it. Bye.
Me not care no more.
Sorry, not interested. I'll be going now.
Me not interested. Me go now.
Lady Aribeth has temporarily assigned me to militia service.
Text: 아리베스 경이 날 일시적으로 민병대 임무에 배치하셨어.

TextEng: Aribeth make me into militia for li'l while.
Alaefin? What can you tell me about him?
Text: 알레핀? 그에 대해 뭘 말해줄 수 있어?

TextEng: Alley-fin? What you know 'bout him?
Text: 알레..르 머요? 그에 대해 뭘 알아?

TextEng: How do I get into the prison, again?
How me get in prison?
Tell me again what the reward will be.
What reward again?
If yous can't do this, why could me?
Text: 너도 못 하는데 내가 왜 할 수 있어?

TextEng: If you can't do it, how would I?
Text: 당신도 못 하는데 내가 어떻게 해?
